data.description: **Low interest rate seller financing available**  Elegantly maintained residence boasting ample parking space. Set amidst a serene backdrop, the property is flanked by two picturesque ponds that infuse tranquility into the surroundings. Both the interior and exterior exhibit recent upgrades with a fresh coat of paint. The home is equipped with central heating and air conditioning to ensure year-round comfort. Inside, new vinyl flooring seamlessly complements the tastefully remodeled kitchen, punctuated by contemporary white vinyl sliding windows.  Adding to the property's allure is a detached studio, meticulously constructed in 2020, situated adjacent to the garage. This space promises versatility, be it for artistic endeavors, a home office, or guest accommodation.  Shasta college is 7 mins away Bethel Church is 7 mins away Shopping and restaurants roughly 10 mins drive.
